text: Please remove this top bar from the eval page

proposedTasks.title: Remove header bar from Eval phase page
proposedTasks.description:
Remove the top header bar from the EvalPhase component (`packages/frontend/src/pages/phases/EvalPhase.tsx`). The bar in question is the `eval-phase-header` div (the `shrink-0 border-b` container) that displays the "Eval" heading and description text. The feedback input and feed should begin at the top of the phase content area.

Acceptance criteria:
- The header div (`data-testid="eval-phase-header"`) and its children (h2 "Eval" + description paragraph) are removed from the component.
- The feedback input card and feedback history remain unchanged and render correctly at the top of the scrollable area.
- No layout regressions  the flex column layout still fills available height and scrolls properly.
- Existing tests that reference `eval-phase-header` are updated or removed accordingly.

taskTitles: Remove header bar from Eval phase page
